OL,3,CPizza giant Domino's to hire 5,000
OL,4,Cextra staff ahead of peak trading
OL,5,Cseason
OL,7,FPizza giant Domino's has said it will
OL,8,Fhire an extra 5,000 people across the
OL,9,FUK and Ireland in the coming months.
OL,11,FThe London-listed company said it is
OL,12,Flooking for delivery drivers, in-store
OL,13,Fstaff and pizza makers to join its
OL,14,F35,000-strong workforce ahead of its
OL,15,Fpeak trading period.
OL,17,FDomino's recorded a drop in orders
OL,18,Fover the first half of 2024, with
OL,19,Fbosses blaming a "slow start" to the
OL,20,Fyear.
