OL,7,FBut in August it said it was
OL,8,Fwitnessing a recovery in customer
OL,9,Fconfidence and that it hoped to drive
OL,10,Fstronger sales with improved pricing.
OL,12,FThe pizza business, which has 1,344
OL,13,Fsites across the UK and Ireland, said
OL,14,Fit has witnessed lower food and energy
OL,15,Fcosts, although these have been offset
OL,16,Fpartly by a rise in the national
OL,17,Fliving wage.
